{"tid":2424624,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"契媽今年沖偏財","createTime":"2021-02-26T17:14:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T15:27:19.000Z","uid":60200,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"92d7b96bc69b8895e7ea28279db5547f667ede99","tid":2424624,"uid":60200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T17:14:17.000Z","msg":"Catherine Duddy Wood，1955年11月26日<br />\n日月年運流<br />\n辛丁乙甲辛<br />\n卯亥未午丑<br />\n<br />\n今年辛丑牛年, 與契媽出身之年天剋地沖, 且沖佢偏財, 原局亥卯未合木被丑土所沖, 因亥卯未是合財局, 現在合財被破, 乙辛沖, 龍逃走, 我預期契媽今年都係冇運行, 資金快速流失, 神話破滅"},{"pid":"26b7679a98bb0ccfd719efa681f7ab117973c6fb","tid":2424624,"uid":59870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T17:17:03.000Z","msg":"係吖？快啲send email話佢知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99b92121e19c5532a62c08a239b03d7433d3b6a5","tid":2424624,"uid":17330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T17:38:03.000Z","msg":"唔識八字，但見佢五行都有，<br />\n其實應該唔會差得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21b0a0e6cfe4931f3dcdd9c582fd4b0097822afc","tid":2424624,"uid":60200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99b92121e19c5532a62c08a239b03d7433d3b6a5","tid":2424624,"uid":17330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T17:38:03.000Z","msg":"唔識八字，但見佢五行都有，<br />\n其實應該唔會差得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T18:02:22.000Z","msg":"所以我剩係話佢今年流年沖財姐, 無話出年"},{"pid":"840653ea6fe767f7a9b7a97d8fac938b17db521f","tid":2424624,"uid":117947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T09:50:59.000Z","msg":"咁今年唔買契媽住"},{"pid":"d9e11a2b9a3138b0abc81949b7d3237d4997d180","tid":2424624,"uid":60200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T15:22:34.000Z","msg":"而家走其實都未遲, 可能仲要跌多50%, 今次納指股災將由ARK系列引起"},{"pid":"ae82ea82ebb7b9d1ab883408951a0ddbb170e1e3","tid":2424624,"uid":387826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score